1. Create Webpack bundle.js file using below command. (this is not ideal approch.)
  >webpack app.ts bundle.js
  alernative solition:-
   a. add webpack.config.js file.(install typescript, webpack and ts-loader -- see in package.json)
   b. run >webpack command. (you can create task in script tag in package.json also)
2. open http server using below command. By default this server run on localhost:8080.
  >http-server
3. open browser and past http://localhost:8080/index.htm URL.

Note- check for tsconfig.json file.
Also we need to configure task runner for converting ts file to js file.(task.json)
  
